---
title: Zesty Fig-Glazed Pork Tenderloin with Buttery Pan Veggies
description: This recipe is the epitome of a sweet and savoury success.  Sweet fig spread glazes over juicy pork tenderloin to ensure that the whole family can get 'figgy' with dinner tonight!

